.Dd $Mdocdate: July 16 2013 $
.Dt LED 4 sparc64
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm led
.Nd SPARC64 LED driver
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "led* at ebus?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the front panel alert LED.
This LED can be made to blink based on the load average on most systems
by setting the
.Xr sysctl 3
variable
.Ar machdep.led_blink
to a non-zero value.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr sysctl 3 ,
.Xr ebus 4 ,
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr sysctl 8
.Sh HISTORY
.Ox
support for the
.Nm
first appeared in
.Ox 4.2 .
